{
  "texts": [
    "An analogous model of retinal stimulation is currently being used to simulate and optimize prosthetic vision in an VR setting 103 by generating training sets for deep learning-based preprocessing 104.",
    "For entities such as the FDA and Medicare, these models can provide insights into what sorts of visual tests/ metrics will be important for evaluating devices.",
    "Finally, for surgeons and patient families, these models will provide more realistic expectations of likely perceptual outcomes.",
    "All data used in this paper were publicly available.",
    "Data are taken from a variety of papers."
  ]
}